snippet.title: SHAKE YOUR MONEY SIMULATOR 2016 - OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
"Shake Your Money Simulator 2016" is the newest spend-money simulation which will teach your wallet to hide money from your eyes. Besides, this is a first game in 2016, where you can finally look at pixel opossum!

Available: March 21, 2016

Steam Link: http://goo.gl/nrwfsG

CrashBieCay's Channel: https://goo.gl/clhFxr
Atria's Channel: https://goo.gl/6EVbHm
